{"type":"message","id":"da79b561","parentId":"1a9f92c3","timestamp":"2026-03-31T17:19:29.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the current status more thoroughly to give a complete answer. First, I'll verify if 1Password is integrated and working, then explain how it works.\n\nActually, I already checked: CLI is installed but not signed in. Let me provide a clear answer about the current state and how it works.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Not set up yet for authentication, but here's how it works and what you need to do:\n\n**Current status:** \n- ✅ 1Password CLI installed (v2.33.1)\n- ❌ Not signed in (no active session)\n- ❌ Desktop app integration not enabled\n\n**How it works (once set up):**\n\n1. **Enable in 1Password app:**\n   - Settings → Security → Enable Linux system auth (fingerprint/password)\n   - Developer → Settings → Check \"Integrate with 1Password CLI\"\n\n2. **Sign in (once per session):**\n   ```bash\n   op signin\n   ```\n   → Uses your system authentication (no master password typed)\n\n3. **Use secrets in OpenClaw:**\n   ```bash\n   op read \"op://Personal/NOTION_KEY/password\"\n   ```\n   → Injects the secret only when needed, never stores it locally\n\n4. **OpenClaw integration:** There's a 1Password skill that lets you:\n   - Read secrets: `op read \"...\"`\n   - Run commands with injected secrets\n   - Manage vaults/items\n\n**Benefits over .env:**\n- Secrets stay encrypted in 1Password vault\n- No plaintext files on disk\n- Automatic locking when 1Password locks\n- Biometric/system auth protection\n- Easy rotation/revocation\n\n**Want to set it up now?** I can guide you through enabling the integration and storing your first key. Or if you prefer keeping .env for now, that's fine too for low-risk keys like Notion/YouTube."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":34965,"output":405,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35370,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774977555967,"responseId":"chatcmpl-aa71c3df14b8ce06"}}
